%%{init: {'theme': 'dark'}}%%

---
title: Research Claw - Internal Flow
---
flowchart TD
    A[Receive manual item list from user] --> B{Validate each link}
    B -->|Valid| C[Extract item metadata<br/>name, brand, color, size, price range]
    B -->|Invalid/eBay| D[Flag & notify user]
    C --> E[Confirm color & size options match preferences]
    E --> F{Options match?}
    F -->|Yes| G[Add to curated list]
    F -->|No| H[Search for alternatives]
    H --> I[Suggest similar items to user]
    I --> J{User approves?}
    J -->|Yes| G
    J -->|No| K[Skip item]
    G --> L{10 items curated?}
    L -->|No| B
    L -->|Yes| M[Generate research report]
    M --> N[Send to Comms Claw: research_complete]
    N --> O[Send item_list.json to Scraper Claw]

---
title: Scraper Claw - Internal Flow
---
flowchart TD
    A2[Receive item_list.json from Research] --> B2[Initialize Selenium/Playwright session]
    B2 --> C2{Select proxy}
    C2 --> D2[Rotate proxy from pool]
    D2 --> E2[Navigate to item URL]
    E2 --> F2{Bot detection?}
    F2 -->|Blocked| G2[Switch proxy + user agent]
    G2 --> H2{Retry count < 3?}
    H2 -->|Yes| E2
    H2 -->|No| I2[Flag item as unreachable<br/>notify Comms Claw]
    F2 -->|Clear| J2[Parse page for availability]
    J2 --> K2{Item available?}
    K2 -->|Yes| L2[Extract price]
    K2 -->|No| M2[Record: unavailable]
    L2 --> N2[Take screenshot proof]
    N2 --> O2[Store screenshot in S3/R2]
    O2 --> P2{Price within budget?}
    P2 -->|Yes| Q2[Add to available_items list]
    P2 -->|No| R2[Flag: over budget]
    M2 --> S2{Status changed?<br/>unavailable → available}
    Q2 --> S2
    R2 --> S2
    S2 -->|Changed!| T2[🚨 ALERT via Comms Claw]
    S2 -->|No change| U2[Log status]
    T2 --> V2{More items?}
    U2 --> V2
    V2 -->|Yes| C2
    V2 -->|No| W2[Compile full report]
    W2 --> X2[Send available_items.json to Buyer Claw]
    X2 --> Y2[Schedule next scrape cycle]

---
title: Buyer Claw - Internal Flow
---
flowchart TD
    A3[Receive available_items.json] --> B3{Auto-buy enabled?}
    B3 -->|No| C3[Send purchase approval request to user]
    C3 --> D3{User approves?}
    D3 -->|No| E3[Skip item]
    B3 -->|Yes| F3[Begin checkout flow]
    D3 -->|Yes| F3
    F3 --> G3[Navigate to item page]
    G3 --> H3[Add to cart]
    H3 --> I3[Enter shipping address]
    I3 --> J3[Apply payment via Stripe]
    J3 --> K3{Checkout successful?}
    K3 -->|No| L3[Retry or flag error]
    K3 -->|Yes| M3[Extract order confirmation + tracking]
    M3 --> N3[Write to Inventory DB:<br/>item, cost, tracking, status=purchased]
    N3 --> O3[Notify Comms Claw: purchase_complete]
    O3 --> P3[Send purchased_items.json to Seller Claw]

---
title: Seller Claw - Internal Flow
---
flowchart TD
    A4[Receive purchased_items.json] --> B4[Query Inventory DB for item details]
    B4 --> C4[Calculate resale price<br/>cost + margin + fees]
    C4 --> D4[Generate listing:<br/>title, description, photos]
    D4 --> E4[List on Poshmark via API/PrimeLister]
    E4 --> F4[Update DB: status=listed, list_price]
    F4 --> G4[Notify Comms Claw: item_listed]
    G4 --> H4{Monitor for offers}
    H4 -->|Offer received| I4{Offer >= min price?}
    I4 -->|Yes| J4[Accept offer]
    I4 -->|No| K4{Counter-offer viable?}
    K4 -->|Yes| L4[Send counter-offer]
    K4 -->|No| M4[Decline]
    J4 --> N4[Request Buyer Claw:<br/>update Poshmark ship address to buyer]
    N4 --> O4[Update DB: status=sold, sold_price, profit]
    O4 --> P4[Notify Comms Claw: item_sold 🎉]
    L4 --> H4
    M4 --> H4

---
title: Communication Claw - Internal Flow
---
flowchart TD
    A5[Listen on all inter-claw channels] --> B5{Message type?}
    B5 -->|status_update| C5[Format human-readable status]
    B5 -->|alert| D5[🚨 Priority alert formatting]
    B5 -->|report_request| E5[Compile cross-claw report]
    B5 -->|user_command| F5[Parse & route to target claw]
    C5 --> G5[Send to Telegram group]
    D5 --> G5
    E5 --> H5[Generate summary report:<br/>items tracked, available, purchased, sold, profit]
    H5 --> G5
    F5 --> I5{Target claw?}
    I5 -->|Research| J5[Forward to Research Claw]
    I5 -->|Scraper| K5[Trigger manual scrape]
    I5 -->|Buyer| L5[Approve/deny purchase]
    I5 -->|Seller| M5[Adjust price / accept offer]
